extends java.lang.Object
    A current replacement for the forge biome dictionary. To register to the biome dictionary, use the event for RegistryEvent.Register<BiomeType>. Please use register(BiomeType) as opposed to IForgeRegistry.register(IForgeRegistryEntry) since I perform special checks to merge entries together.

    To add support for your mod without needing the API as a dependency, create a method in your main mod class like this one StructureGelMod.getBiomesSG().

    When using a ConfigTemplates.StructureConfig and adding biome tags to the config, it will reference this dictionary.
